WEBVTT

00:09:57.320 --> 00:10:02.656
e comprobar como os estadounidenses 
van vendo certas palabras emparelladas

00:10:02.680 --> 00:10:05.176
a medida que van medrando
na súa sociedade

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:09.176
Así, cando aparece a palabra "negro"
na cultura estadounidense,

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:11.256
de que vai acompañada?

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:12.696
"Pobre",

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:13.936
"violento",

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:15.296
"relixioso",

00:10:15.320 --> 00:10:16.536
"preguiceiro",

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:17.776
"alegre",

00:10:17.800 --> 00:10:19.536
"perigoso".

00:10:19.560 --> 00:10:21.056
Cando aparece "branco",

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:23.476
as palabras frecuentemente
emparelladas son

00:10:23.476 --> 00:10:24.696
"rico",

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:25.976
"progresista",

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:27.200
"convencional"

00:10:28.120 --> 00:10:29.336
"perseverante",

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:30.576
"exitoso"